double-dipped in gold!

287
00:10:48,357 --> 00:10:51,109
Unless | get a written
apology.

288
00:10:53,278 --> 00:10:54,571
[ ding!]
Huh?

289
00:10:54,655 --> 00:10:56,240
Gold piece.

290
00:10:56,323 --> 00:10:59,076
